            ; there were three Ten pounds in that name; that was all that was made out that day; that note is counter sign'd.</p>
               <p>Council for the crown. Did you counter sign any note to any body that day No 344.</p>
               <p>Lambert. To 
               <persName id="t17710911-39-person388">
                  James
                   Milner
               <interp inst="t17710911-39-person388" type="surname" value="Milner"></interp>
