               <p>Q. By whom was that note signed?</p>
               <p>Lambert. By one Saberton, payable to 
               <persName id="t17710911-39-person389">
                  James
                   Milner
               <interp inst="t17710911-39-person389" type="surname" value="Milner"></interp>
